OL,4,G1850FLocation, Location, Location
OL,5,     GKirstie Allsopp and Phil Spencer
OL,6,     Ghouse-hunt in London the week
OL,7,     Gafter the Brexit vote. Sisters
OL,8,     GRuth and Anna pool their funds,
OL,9,     Gwhile Aba has champagne tastes
OL,10,     Gbut lemonade money.
