OL,4,G2100F24 Hours in A&E
OL,5,     GLeslie, who's 75, is rushed to
OL,6,     GA&E with a suspected stroke.
OL,7,     GHannah, who's 37, has pain in her
OL,8,     Gspine after falling from her
OL,9,     Ghorse. And Isabella, who's six,
OL,10,     Ghas hurt her neck.
OL,11,G2200F24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     GMark, who's 32, is rushed to St
OL,13,     GGeorge's with a head injury after
OL,14,     Ghaving an epileptic seizure.
OL,15,     GAnastasia, who's 80, has a severe
OL,16,     Gpain in her leg and is sent for
OL,17,     Gan X-ray.
